  "What does 'vacancy rate' mean for rental properties?": "",
  "The discount offered to attract new tenants": "",
  "The percentage of time a property is occupied by tenants": "",
  "The percentage of time a rental unit is unoccupied and not generating income": "",
  "The number of rooms in a property that are unused": "",
